13253c14-ea22-4288-9bc3-1da4b42c42bd.title: <player>
13253c14-ea22-4288-9bc3-1da4b42c42bd.text: It's okay, I'm here to help you.

424e4ad2-3d0f-4ab6-87ad-49d437cd2081.title: <player>
424e4ad2-3d0f-4ab6-87ad-49d437cd2081.text:
No, honest. I helped the alchemists, but I had no idea
what their plans involved.

aa45b8c3-db6a-427d-8dfa-c6cacf99b630.title: Homunculus
aa45b8c3-db6a-427d-8dfa-c6cacf99b630.text:
Arggh, so alchemist create me now I trapped for
experiements. But still I confused.

f239aefc-6074-4eec-8ac2-a1222f1fada7.title: Homunculus
f239aefc-6074-4eec-8ac2-a1222f1fada7.text: Me see logic, feeeel magic. A mix of the two.

62695471-4066-40f1-afed-ae8b9a3c4362.title: <player>
62695471-4066-40f1-afed-ae8b9a3c4362.text: Hmmm. A creature created of logic and magic.

5a25bc56-a7eb-4b40-807e-388d506509e6.title: <player>
5a25bc56-a7eb-4b40-807e-388d506509e6.text: Don't fear. I shall fix your mind!

4aaac068-c162-40a0-b347-bd0ef57a0529.title: Homunculus
4aaac068-c162-40a0-b347-bd0ef57a0529.text: No so sure it is easy to do. No one canna 'elp. Arghhh.

e9735c8e-800a-4614-87a1-bbb1510a575d.text:
You must now make sense of the Homunculus's mind. Force him to
either follow the line of logic or the line of magic.

981d1722-7e90-4dc5-b702-65a8d47f3465.title: <player>
981d1722-7e90-4dc5-b702-65a8d47f3465.text:
You tell me that you're confused, so ask me some
questions!

options.text: Get some logs and a tinderbox.
With the aid of 5 fire runes.
That's impossible! No one can do that!
Not too sure, I've never seen it happen.
With the help of the magical dragonstones!
By ignition of gas in their belly as they exhale.
Runecraft, enchant jewellery, perform alchemy.
Eat, sleep, nothing that exciting.
Fletching, Crafting, Smithing.
Bury them.
I'd like to think you wouldn't be carrying bones around.
Turn them into bananas or peaches!
I'm not really much of a traveller, sorry.
Run, run as fast as you can.
Depends where you are headed, but teleport spells are a safe bet.
Yes, you can make magic potions to boost your skills.
People mix together ingredients in vials. The nutrients will help you.
Yes, liquid-filled vials. Big deal.
By harnessing the power of the gods!
Never seen one personally.
Take some essence to an altar and use a talisman.
Perhaps. I've never seen it myself, though.
Yep, you can use the Telekinetic Grab spell.
Sure. Use your brain to tell someone to move it!
Through the power of alchemy.
It's beyond me!
It's a simple case of combining materials.
You have special powers - no surprise seeing how you were created.
Coincidence - there is a lot of loose metal around.
Yeah, they were cool! Nice one.
Try some Mining followed by Smithing.
How about Magic and Runecrafting?
That's up to you; depends on what you find interesting.
Don't be silly! You'd get burnt!
Can't see why not, anything is possible.
Well the sun is not actually there, it's where it used to be!
Everything has a reason, even if you don't know what it is.
Probably a bit of both.
Your very existense speaks of mystical forces.
Magic.
I'm too laid back to really care, mate.
Logic.

09e08869-2fcf-4c5d-b04c-def70f4b0dc9.title: Homunculus
09e08869-2fcf-4c5d-b04c-def70f4b0dc9.text: That it! Make sense now, thank you!

b17cd999-c350-4941-8290-0e12b5d82855.title: <player>
b17cd999-c350-4941-8290-0e12b5d82855.text: I decided to root for logic.

35aeecc8-b17d-45b8-be15-3678be0909e3.title: Homunculus
35aeecc8-b17d-45b8-be15-3678be0909e3.text:
No does matter which you chose. Me needed organise
my thoughts. I see there is truth in both.

47364e65-6c61-4086-bcc1-0351408b9c08.title: Homunculus
47364e65-6c61-4086-bcc1-0351408b9c08.text:
Now we go scare alchemies - they have been wrong to
do this! Although I have life, they mustn't go about this
again.

9c31ca9a-2647-46c5-9fd2-832076dfab63.title: <player>
9c31ca9a-2647-46c5-9fd2-832076dfab63.text: Sounds like a good plan. Can you get out of that cage?

75f36963-4730-491a-be3f-a33791e16538.title: Homunculus
75f36963-4730-491a-be3f-a33791e16538.text:
Easy. You run down and I watching from here. I
surprise right moment.

32a10651-b1de-4929-9a17-89608302fbd4.title: <player>
32a10651-b1de-4929-9a17-89608302fbd4.text: I decided to root for magic.

5cf4b951-632e-4788-aba9-bb8a97b5270d.title: Homunculus
5cf4b951-632e-4788-aba9-bb8a97b5270d.text:
Better. You been mine angel. I now have the
understanding I need.

d5b35c3d-b9e8-4716-86dd-be791afb7008.title: Homunculus
d5b35c3d-b9e8-4716-86dd-be791afb7008.text: Please, alchemists you speak, me appear to surprise.

aa34e6d4-833f-47b1-b080-9b7e4c713b1c.title: <player>
aa34e6d4-833f-47b1-b080-9b7e4c713b1c.text:
I'm not sure I understand, but okay, I will go have a
word with them.

808a3ac4-3786-4802-afb6-03240d275320.title: Homunculus
808a3ac4-3786-4802-afb6-03240d275320.text: Me do know. Pleased you rescue.

86af9442-7b5f-42df-88da-fe6909f53a95.title: <player>
86af9442-7b5f-42df-88da-fe6909f53a95.text: My pleasure. So what is this place?

0885233a-ab01-4309-a378-9faf973a09b1.title: Homunculus
0885233a-ab01-4309-a378-9faf973a09b1.text:
They use essence of Guthix power. Create tower pump
this from ground. Make me with godly power.
Dangerous.

d3a558cb-5328-4d20-87e7-a179a185e800.title: <player>
d3a558cb-5328-4d20-87e7-a179a185e800.text:
Oh dear, but you're okay now. You have this place to
reside in.

51226899-a34c-4c65-8820-f4db03eae4e0.title: Homunculus
51226899-a34c-4c65-8820-f4db03eae4e0.text:
Thrank you. For reward you speak me, I makes
monsters.

5ad710d1-9f4f-4d79-9189-e9503bb2ab6f.title: <player>
5ad710d1-9f4f-4d79-9189-e9503bb2ab6f.text:
Hi there, you mentioned something about creating
monsters...?

71b6df1b-626f-457b-8faf-7a011516de87.title: Homunculus
71b6df1b-626f-457b-8faf-7a011516de87.text:
Good! I gain know from alchemists and builders. Me
make beings.

3069a427-2ca8-4ab7-b01f-cc43d17b14d4.title: <player>
3069a427-2ca8-4ab7-b01f-cc43d17b14d4.text:
Interesting. Tell me if I'm right. By the alchemists and
builders creating you, you have inherited their combined
knowledge in much the same way that a child might
inherit the looks of their parents.

ab451cec-d53f-4858-ae38-aa0ebaf2098b.title: <player>
ab451cec-d53f-4858-ae38-aa0ebaf2098b.text: So what do you need me to do?

58e6d3e5-0288-45cf-a95f-a763d82d6017.title: Homunculus
58e6d3e5-0288-45cf-a95f-a763d82d6017.text:
Inspect symbol of life altars around dungeon. You see
item give. Use item on altar. Activate altar to create,
you fight.
